    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice</strong> and 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [500ml] </span><strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-copy-10-1680704080694-x200.jpg",
