        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>aubergine </strong>and cook for 6-7 min or until it's beginning to brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-7-1680704090707-x200.jpg",
