          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the aubergine is cooking, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, keeping the whites and greens separate</p><p>Top, tail and grate your <strong>radishes</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
