      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the aubergine has browned, reduce the heat to medium, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>agave</strong> and <strong>mirin</strong> and cook for 2 min or until a sticky sauce has formed – this is your <strong>teriyaki aubergine</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
