      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> grated radishes </strong>and <strong>spring onion whites </strong>(reserve the greens for garnish!) in a bowl with your <strong>vegan mayo</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> radish slaw</strong></p>",
