    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>basmati</strong> <strong>rice</strong> between bowls with the<strong> teriyaki aubergine</strong>,<strong> radish slaw</strong> and <strong>kale seaweed</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> sliced spring onion greens</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
